Package org.dessertj.modules.jpms

Module API implementation for the Java Platform Module System.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    JavaPlatformModuleResolver
    A ModuleResolver that scans the class-path for module-info classes.
    JpmsModule
    The information within a module-info.class represented as ModuleSlice.
    JpmsModuleRequirement
    Represents a module required by a JpmsModule.

Package org.dessertj.modules.jpms Description

Module API implementation for the Java Platform Module System. Provides the information within module-info classes by JpmsModule objects that implement the ModuleSlice interface.
